== 製作 ==
有一陣子，[[馬田·史高西斯|馬田·史高西斯]]曾想執導<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jo-nesbo-working-title-greenlight-264392 |title = Martin Scorsese to Direct 'The Snowman' for Working Title |author = Scott Roxborough |date = 2011-11-21 |publisher = The Hollywood Reporter |language = en}}</ref>，不過他在2013年退出<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://screenrant.com/snowman-movie-director-martin-scorsese-jo-nesbo/ |title = Martin Scorsese Will Not Direct ‘The Snowman’ |author = Kyle Hembree |date = 2013-04-16 |publisher = Screenrant |language = en}}</ref>。第二年，[[湯瑪士·艾佛遜|湯瑪士·艾佛遜]]被聘請執導本片。在艾佛遜之前，製片商曾經考慮[[摩丹·泰頓|摩丹·泰頓]]和[[巴塔萨·科马库|巴塔萨·科马库]]成為導演，但兩人都婉拒了。到2015年9月，[[麥可·法斯賓達|麥可·法斯賓達]]正在談判加入本片的主要角色。[[蕾貝卡·弗格森|蕾貝卡·弗格森]]和[[夏綠蒂·甘絲柏|夏綠蒂·甘絲柏]]分別在10月和12月進行談判。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://deadline.com/2015/10/rebecca-ferguson-michael-fassbender-snowman-jo-nesbo-prometheus-gambit-mission-impossible-1201581418/ |title = Rebecca Ferguson In Talks To Star In ‘The Snowman’ Opposite Michael Fassbender; Eyeing Other Big Roles |author = Ali Jaafar |date = 2015-10-14 |publisher = deadline.com |language = en}}</ref>

